<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> بابُ صِفَةِ أَبْوَابِ الجَنَّةِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> <span class="c2">«مَنْ أَنْفَقَ زَوْجَيْنِ دُعِيَ مِنْ باب الجَنَّةِ»</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فِيهِ عُبَادَةُ، عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>